short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension replaces the default chrome tab with discontinued Inbox by Google sunshine background.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Sunshine Tab is an extension that replaces the default chrome tab with the the discontinued Inbox by Google background whenever your inbox was empty

This extension is meant to bright up your day just a a little.
